### EasyReads API Tests
### This file can be used with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = your-firebase-id-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Verify Token (requires Firebase ID token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User Info (requires Firebase ID token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

